=== Ubuntu 12.04 translation contributors ===

This list represents the individuals who have contributed directly or indirectly to translating Ubuntu 12.04 LTS in each of the languages it is available. As such, both contributions done through Launchpad Translations, Ubuntu's online translation platform, and through external projects have been counted, as well as those contributions done in past releases that are still used in the current release. <nowiki>[[http://people.canonical.com/~dpm/stats/ubuntu-12.04-translation-stats.html|Learn in how many languages Ubuntu is available ›]]</nowiki>

Over '''17 thousand translators''' contributed to this release. Thank you for making Ubuntu in your language possible!
